Quarter: The fiscal quarter and year for which the compliance rate is being reported. This helps to track compliance over time.
Compliance_Rate: The percentage of third-party vendors in compliance during the specified quarter. This is crucial for assessing vendor risk and guiding regulation implementation.
Regulation_Impact: A brief description of how the compliance rate affects regulatory actions and security measures. This provides context for cybersecurity decision-makers.
